115 uint16_t
116 cm_uint16_from_m_float(float m)
117 {
118  if (m < 0.0f) {
119  return 0;
120 
121  } else if (m > 655.35f) {
122  return 65535;
123  }
124 
125  return (uint16_t)(m * 100.0f);
126 }

128 void get_mavlink_navigation_mode(const struct vehicle_status_s *const status, uint8_t *mavlink_base_mode,
129  union px4_custom_mode *custom_mode)
130 {
131  custom_mode->data = 0;
132  *mavlink_base_mode = 0;
133 
134  /* HIL */
135  if (status->hil_state == vehicle_status_s::HIL_STATE_ON) {
136  *mavlink_base_mode |= MAV_MODE_FLAG_HIL_ENABLED;
137  }
138 
139  /* arming state */
140  if (status->arming_state == vehicle_status_s::ARMING_STATE_ARMED) {
141  *mavlink_base_mode |= MAV_MODE_FLAG_SAFETY_ARMED;
142  }
143 
144  /* main state */
145  *mavlink_base_mode |= MAV_MODE_FLAG_CUSTOM_MODE_ENABLED;
146 
147  const uint8_t auto_mode_flags = MAV_MODE_FLAG_AUTO_ENABLED
148  | MAV_MODE_FLAG_STABILIZE_ENABLED
149  | MAV_MODE_FLAG_GUIDED_ENABLED;
150 
151  switch (status->nav_state) {
152  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_MANUAL:
153  *mavlink_base_mode |= MAV_MODE_FLAG_MANUAL_INPUT_ENABLED
154  | (status->is_rotary_wing ? MAV_MODE_FLAG_STABILIZE_ENABLED : 0);
155  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_MANUAL;
156  break;
157 
158  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_ACRO:
159  *mavlink_base_mode |= MAV_MODE_FLAG_MANUAL_INPUT_ENABLED;
160  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_ACRO;
161  break;
162 
163  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_RATTITUDE:
164  *mavlink_base_mode |= MAV_MODE_FLAG_MANUAL_INPUT_ENABLED;
165  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_RATTITUDE;
166  break;
167 
168  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_STAB:
169  *mavlink_base_mode |= MAV_MODE_FLAG_MANUAL_INPUT_ENABLED
170  | MAV_MODE_FLAG_STABILIZE_ENABLED;
171  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_STABILIZED;
172  break;
173 
174  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_ALTCTL:
175  *mavlink_base_mode |= MAV_MODE_FLAG_MANUAL_INPUT_ENABLED
176  | MAV_MODE_FLAG_STABILIZE_ENABLED;
177  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_ALTCTL;
178  break;
179 
180  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_POSCTL:
181  *mavlink_base_mode |= MAV_MODE_FLAG_MANUAL_INPUT_ENABLED
182  | MAV_MODE_FLAG_STABILIZE_ENABLED
183  | MAV_MODE_FLAG_GUIDED_ENABLED; // TODO: is POSCTL GUIDED?
184  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_POSCTL;
185  break;
186 
187  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_AUTO_TAKEOFF:
188  *mavlink_base_mode |= auto_mode_flags;
189  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_AUTO;
190  custom_mode->sub_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_SUB_MODE_AUTO_TAKEOFF;
191  break;
192 
193  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_AUTO_MISSION:
194  *mavlink_base_mode |= auto_mode_flags;
195  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_AUTO;
196  custom_mode->sub_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_SUB_MODE_AUTO_MISSION;
197  break;
198 
199  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_AUTO_LOITER:
200  *mavlink_base_mode |= auto_mode_flags;
201  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_AUTO;
202  custom_mode->sub_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_SUB_MODE_AUTO_LOITER;
203  break;
204 
205  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_AUTO_FOLLOW_TARGET:
206  *mavlink_base_mode |= auto_mode_flags;
207  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_AUTO;
208  custom_mode->sub_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_SUB_MODE_AUTO_FOLLOW_TARGET;
209  break;
210 
211  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_AUTO_PRECLAND:
212  *mavlink_base_mode |= auto_mode_flags;
213  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_AUTO;
214  custom_mode->sub_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_SUB_MODE_AUTO_PRECLAND;
215  break;
216 
217  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_AUTO_RTL:
218 
219  /* fallthrough */
220  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_AUTO_RCRECOVER:
221  *mavlink_base_mode |= auto_mode_flags;
222  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_AUTO;
223  custom_mode->sub_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_SUB_MODE_AUTO_RTL;
224  break;
225 
226  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_AUTO_LAND:
227  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_AUTO_LANDENGFAIL:
228  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_AUTO_LANDGPSFAIL:
229 
230  /* fallthrough */
231  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_DESCEND:
232  *mavlink_base_mode |= auto_mode_flags;
233  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_AUTO;
234  custom_mode->sub_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_SUB_MODE_AUTO_LAND;
235  break;
236 
237  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_AUTO_RTGS:
238  *mavlink_base_mode |= auto_mode_flags;
239  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_AUTO;
240  custom_mode->sub_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_SUB_MODE_AUTO_RTGS;
241  break;
242 
243  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_TERMINATION:
244  *mavlink_base_mode |= MAV_MODE_FLAG_MANUAL_INPUT_ENABLED;
245  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_MANUAL;
246  break;
247 
248  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_OFFBOARD:
249  *mavlink_base_mode |= auto_mode_flags;
250  custom_mode->main_mode = PX4_CUSTOM_MAIN_MODE_OFFBOARD;
251  break;
252 
253  case vehicle_status_s::NAVIGATION_STATE_MAX:
254  /* this is an unused case, ignore */
255  break;
256 
257  }
258 }

260 void get_mavlink_mode_state(const struct vehicle_status_s *const status, uint8_t *mavlink_state,
261  uint8_t *mavlink_base_mode, uint32_t *mavlink_custom_mode)
262 {
263  *mavlink_state = 0;
264  *mavlink_base_mode = 0;
265  *mavlink_custom_mode = 0;
266 
267  union px4_custom_mode custom_mode;
268  get_mavlink_navigation_mode(status, mavlink_base_mode, &custom_mode);
269  *mavlink_custom_mode = custom_mode.data;
270 
271  /* set system state */
272  if (status->arming_state == vehicle_status_s::ARMING_STATE_INIT
273  || status->arming_state == vehicle_status_s::ARMING_STATE_IN_AIR_RESTORE
274  || status->arming_state == vehicle_status_s::ARMING_STATE_STANDBY_ERROR) { // TODO review
275  *mavlink_state = MAV_STATE_UNINIT;
276 
277  } else if (status->arming_state == vehicle_status_s::ARMING_STATE_ARMED) {
278  *mavlink_state = MAV_STATE_ACTIVE;
279 
280  } else if (status->arming_state == vehicle_status_s::ARMING_STATE_STANDBY) {
281  *mavlink_state = MAV_STATE_STANDBY;
282 
283  } else if (status->arming_state == vehicle_status_s::ARMING_STATE_REBOOT) {
284  *mavlink_state = MAV_STATE_POWEROFF;
285 
286  } else {
287  *mavlink_state = MAV_STATE_CRITICAL;
288  }
289 }

324

326  {
327  return true;
328  }
329 
330 private:
331  MavlinkOrbSubscription *_status_sub;
332 
333  /* do not allow top copying this class */
334  MavlinkStreamHeartbeat(MavlinkStreamHeartbeat &) = delete;
335  MavlinkStreamHeartbeat &operator = (const MavlinkStreamHeartbeat &) = delete;
336 
337 protected:
338  explicit MavlinkStreamHeartbeat(Mavlink *mavlink) : MavlinkStream(mavlink),
339  _status_sub(_mavlink->add_orb_subscription(ORB_ID(vehicle_status)))
340  {}
341 
342  bool send(const hrt_abstime t)
343  {
344  struct vehicle_status_s status = {};
345 
346  /* always send the heartbeat, independent of the update status of the topics */
347  if (!_status_sub->update(&status)) {
348  /* if topic update failed fill it with defaults */
349  memset(&status, 0, sizeof(status));
350  }
351 
352  uint8_t base_mode = 0;
353  uint32_t custom_mode = 0;
354  uint8_t system_status = 0;
355  get_mavlink_mode_state(&status, &system_status, &base_mode, &custom_mode);
356 
357  mavlink_msg_heartbeat_send(_mavlink->get_channel(), _mavlink->get_system_type(), MAV_AUTOPILOT_PX4,
358  base_mode, custom_mode, system_status);
359 
360  return true;
361  }
362 };

404  {}
405 
406  bool send(const hrt_abstime t)
407  {
408  if (!_mavlink->get_logbuffer()->empty() && _mavlink->is_connected()) {
409 
410  struct mavlink_log_s mavlink_log = {};
411 
412  if (_mavlink->get_logbuffer()->get(&mavlink_log)) {
413 
414  mavlink_statustext_t msg;
415  msg.severity = mavlink_log.severity;
416  strncpy(msg.text, (const char *)mavlink_log.text, sizeof(msg.text));
417  msg.text[sizeof(msg.text) - 1] = '\0';
418 
419  mavlink_msg_statustext_send_struct(_mavlink->get_channel(), &msg);
420 
421  return true;
422  }
423  }
424 
425  return false;
426  }

472  {}

474  bool send(const hrt_abstime t)
475  {
476  struct vehicle_command_s cmd;
477  bool sent = false;
478 
479  if (_cmd_sub->update_if_changed(&cmd)) {
480 
481  if (!cmd.from_external) {
482  PX4_DEBUG("sending command %d to %d/%d", cmd.command, cmd.target_system, cmd.target_component);
483 
484  MavlinkCommandSender::instance().handle_vehicle_command(cmd, _mavlink->get_channel());
485  sent = true;
486 
487  } else {
488  PX4_DEBUG("not forwarding command %d to %d/%d", cmd.command, cmd.target_system, cmd.target_component);
489  }
490  }
491 
492  MavlinkCommandSender::instance().check_timeout(_mavlink->get_channel());
493 
494  return sent;
495  }

531 private:
532  MavlinkOrbSubscription *_status_sub;
533  MavlinkOrbSubscription *_cpuload_sub;
534  MavlinkOrbSubscription *_battery_status_sub;
535 
536  uint64_t _status_timestamp{0};
537  uint64_t _cpuload_timestamp{0};
538  uint64_t _battery_status_timestamp{0};
539 
540  /* do not allow top copying this class */
541  MavlinkStreamSysStatus(MavlinkStreamSysStatus &) = delete;
542  MavlinkStreamSysStatus &operator = (const MavlinkStreamSysStatus &) = delete;
543 
544 protected:
545  explicit MavlinkStreamSysStatus(Mavlink *mavlink) : MavlinkStream(mavlink),
546  _status_sub(_mavlink->add_orb_subscription(ORB_ID(vehicle_status))),
547  _cpuload_sub(_mavlink->add_orb_subscription(ORB_ID(cpuload))),
548  _battery_status_sub(_mavlink->add_orb_subscription(ORB_ID(battery_status)))
549  {}
550 
551  bool send(const hrt_abstime t)
552  {
553  vehicle_status_s status = {};
554  cpuload_s cpuload = {};
555  battery_status_s battery_status = {};
556 
557  const bool updated_status = _status_sub->update(&_status_timestamp, &status);
558  const bool updated_cpuload = _cpuload_sub->update(&_cpuload_timestamp, &cpuload);
559  const bool updated_battery = _battery_status_sub->update(&_battery_status_timestamp, &battery_status);
560 
561  if (updated_status || updated_battery || updated_cpuload) {
562  mavlink_sys_status_t msg = {};
563 
564  msg.onboard_control_sensors_present = status.onboard_control_sensors_present;
565  msg.onboard_control_sensors_enabled = status.onboard_control_sensors_enabled;
566  msg.onboard_control_sensors_health = status.onboard_control_sensors_health;
567  msg.load = cpuload.load * 1000.0f;
568  msg.voltage_battery = (battery_status.connected) ? battery_status.voltage_filtered_v * 1000.0f : UINT16_MAX;
569  msg.current_battery = (battery_status.connected) ? battery_status.current_filtered_a * 100.0f : -1;
570  msg.battery_remaining = (battery_status.connected) ? ceilf(battery_status.remaining * 100.0f) : -1;
571  // TODO: fill in something useful in the fields below
572  msg.drop_rate_comm = 0;
573  msg.errors_comm = 0;
574  msg.errors_count1 = 0;
575  msg.errors_count2 = 0;
576  msg.errors_count3 = 0;
577  msg.errors_count4 = 0;
578 
579  mavlink_msg_sys_status_send_struct(_mavlink->get_channel(), &msg);
580 
581  /* battery status message with higher resolution */
582  mavlink_battery_status_t bat_msg = {};
583  bat_msg.id = 0;
584  bat_msg.battery_function = MAV_BATTERY_FUNCTION_ALL;
585  bat_msg.type = MAV_BATTERY_TYPE_LIPO;
586  bat_msg.current_consumed = (battery_status.connected) ? battery_status.discharged_mah : -1;
587  bat_msg.energy_consumed = -1;
588  bat_msg.current_battery = (battery_status.connected) ? battery_status.current_filtered_a * 100 : -1;
589  bat_msg.battery_remaining = (battery_status.connected) ? ceilf(battery_status.remaining * 100.0f) : -1;
590  bat_msg.temperature = (battery_status.connected) ? (int16_t)battery_status.temperature : INT16_MAX;
591  //bat_msg.average_current_battery = (battery_status.connected) ? battery_status.average_current_a * 100.0f : -1;
592  //bat_msg.serial_number = (battery_status.connected) ? battery_status.serial_number : 0;
593  //bat_msg.capacity = (battery_status.connected) ? battery_status.capacity : 0;
594  //bat_msg.cycle_count = (battery_status.connected) ? battery_status.cycle_count : UINT16_MAX;
595  //bat_msg.run_time_to_empty = (battery_status.connected) ? battery_status.run_time_to_empty * 60 : 0;
596  //bat_msg.average_time_to_empty = (battery_status.connected) ? battery_status.average_time_to_empty * 60 : 0;
597 
598  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < (sizeof(bat_msg.voltages) / sizeof(bat_msg.voltages[0])); i++) {
599  if ((int)i < battery_status.cell_count && battery_status.connected) {
600  bat_msg.voltages[i] = (battery_status.voltage_v / battery_status.cell_count) * 1000.0f;
601 
602  } else {
603  bat_msg.voltages[i] = UINT16_MAX;
604  }
605  }
606

608 
609  return true;
610  }

612  return false;

652  uint64_t _sensor_time;
653 
654  MavlinkOrbSubscription *_bias_sub;
655  MavlinkOrbSubscription *_differential_pressure_sub;
656  MavlinkOrbSubscription *_magnetometer_sub;
657  MavlinkOrbSubscription *_air_data_sub;
658 
659  uint64_t _accel_timestamp;
660  uint64_t _gyro_timestamp;
661  uint64_t _mag_timestamp;
662  uint64_t _baro_timestamp;
663  uint64_t _dpres_timestamp;
664 
665  /* do not allow top copying this class */
666  MavlinkStreamHighresIMU(MavlinkStreamHighresIMU &) = delete;
667  MavlinkStreamHighresIMU &operator = (const MavlinkStreamHighresIMU &) = delete;
668 
669 protected:
670  explicit MavlinkStreamHighresIMU(Mavlink *mavlink) : MavlinkStream(mavlink),
671  _sensor_sub(_mavlink->add_orb_subscription(ORB_ID(sensor_combined))),
672  _sensor_time(0),
673  _bias_sub(_mavlink->add_orb_subscription(ORB_ID(sensor_bias))),
674  _differential_pressure_sub(_mavlink->add_orb_subscription(ORB_ID(differential_pressure))),
675  _magnetometer_sub(_mavlink->add_orb_subscription(ORB_ID(vehicle_magnetometer))),
676  _air_data_sub(_mavlink->add_orb_subscription(ORB_ID(vehicle_air_data))),
677  _accel_timestamp(0),
678  _gyro_timestamp(0),
679  _mag_timestamp(0),
680  _baro_timestamp(0),
681  _dpres_timestamp(0)
682  {}
683 
684  bool send(const hrt_abstime t)
685  {
686  sensor_combined_s sensor;
687 
688  if (_sensor_sub->update(&_sensor_time, &sensor)) {
689  uint16_t fields_updated = 0;
690 
691  if (_accel_timestamp != sensor.timestamp + sensor.accelerometer_timestamp_relative) {
692  /* mark first three dimensions as changed */
693  fields_updated |= (1 << 0) | (1 << 1) | (1 << 2);
694  _accel_timestamp = sensor.timestamp + sensor.accelerometer_timestamp_relative;
695  }
696 
697  if (_gyro_timestamp != sensor.timestamp) {
698  /* mark second group dimensions as changed */
699  fields_updated |= (1 << 3) | (1 << 4) | (1 << 5);
700  _gyro_timestamp = sensor.timestamp;
701  }
702 
703  vehicle_magnetometer_s magnetometer = {};
704  _magnetometer_sub->update(&magnetometer);
705 
706  if (_mag_timestamp != magnetometer.timestamp) {
707  /* mark third group dimensions as changed */
708  fields_updated |= (1 << 6) | (1 << 7) | (1 << 8);
709  _mag_timestamp = magnetometer.timestamp;
710  }
711 
712  vehicle_air_data_s air_data = {};
713  _air_data_sub->update(&air_data);
714 
715  if (_baro_timestamp != air_data.timestamp) {
716  /* mark fourth group (baro fields) dimensions as changed */
717  fields_updated |= (1 << 9) | (1 << 11) | (1 << 12);
718  _baro_timestamp = air_data.timestamp;
719  }
720 
721  sensor_bias_s bias = {};
722  _bias_sub->update(&bias);
723 
724  differential_pressure_s differential_pressure = {};
725  _differential_pressure_sub->update(&differential_pressure);
726 
727  if (_dpres_timestamp != differential_pressure.timestamp) {
728  /* mark fourth group (dpres field) dimensions as changed */
729  fields_updated |= (1 << 10);
730  _dpres_timestamp = differential_pressure.timestamp;
731  }
732 
733  mavlink_highres_imu_t msg = {};
734 
735  msg.time_usec = sensor.timestamp;
736  msg.xacc = sensor.accelerometer_m_s2[0] - bias.accel_x_bias;
737  msg.yacc = sensor.accelerometer_m_s2[1] - bias.accel_y_bias;
738  msg.zacc = sensor.accelerometer_m_s2[2] - bias.accel_z_bias;
739  msg.xgyro = sensor.gyro_rad[0] - bias.gyro_x_bias;
740  msg.ygyro = sensor.gyro_rad[1] - bias.gyro_y_bias;
741  msg.zgyro = sensor.gyro_rad[2] - bias.gyro_z_bias;
742  msg.xmag = magnetometer.magnetometer_ga[0] - bias.mag_x_bias;
743  msg.ymag = magnetometer.magnetometer_ga[1] - bias.mag_y_bias;
744  msg.zmag = magnetometer.magnetometer_ga[2] - bias.mag_z_bias;
745  msg.abs_pressure = air_data.baro_pressure_pa;
746  msg.diff_pressure = differential_pressure.differential_pressure_raw_pa;
747  msg.pressure_alt = air_data.baro_alt_meter;
748  msg.temperature = air_data.baro_temp_celcius;
749  msg.fields_updated = fields_updated;
750 
751  mavlink_msg_highres_imu_send_struct(_mavlink->get_channel(), &msg);
752 
753  return true;
754  }
755 
756  return false;
757  }

1253

1255  updated |= _pos_sub->update(&_pos_time, &pos);

1261  msg.airspeed = airspeed.indicated_airspeed_m_s;
1262  msg.groundspeed = sqrtf(pos.vx * pos.vx + pos.vy * pos.vy);
1263  msg.heading = math::degrees(wrap_2pi(pos.yaw));
1264

1266  actuator_controls_s act0 = {};
1267  actuator_controls_s act1 = {};
1268  _act0_sub->update(&act0);
1269  _act1_sub->update(&act1);

1271  // VFR_HUD throttle should only be used for operator feedback.
1272  // VTOLs switch between actuator_controls_0 and actuator_controls_1. During transition there isn't a
1273  // a single throttle value, but this should still be a useful heuristic for operator awareness.
1274  //
1275  // Use ACTUATOR_CONTROL_TARGET if accurate states are needed.

1277  act0.control[actuator_controls_s::INDEX_THROTTLE],
1278  act1.control[actuator_controls_s::INDEX_THROTTLE]);
1279

1291

1294  msg.alt = air_data.baro_alt_meter;
1295  }
1296  }
1297 
1298  if (pos.v_z_valid) {
1299  msg.climb = -pos.vz;
1300  }
1301

1305  }

1932  bool lpos_updated = _lpos_sub->update(&_lpos_time, &lpos);
1933 
1934  if (gpos_updated && lpos_updated) {
1935  mavlink_global_position_int_t msg = {};

1938  msg.alt = (-lpos.z + lpos.ref_alt) * 1000.0f;

1943  _air_data_sub->update(&air_data);

1959  }
1960 
1961  } else {

1963  msg.relative_alt = -lpos.z * 1000.0f;
1964  }
1965  }
1966

1968  msg.lat = gpos.lat * 1e7;
1969  msg.lon = gpos.lon * 1e7;
1970 
1971  msg.vx = lpos.vx * 100.0f;
1972  msg.vy = lpos.vy * 100.0f;
1973  msg.vz = lpos.vz * 100.0f;
1974 
1975  msg.hdg = math::degrees(wrap_2pi(lpos.yaw)) * 100.0f;
1976 
1977  mavlink_msg_global_position_int_send_struct(_mavlink->get_channel(), &msg);

2690 private:

2692 
2693  MavlinkOrbSubscription *_act_sub;
2694  uint64_t _act_time;
2695 
2696  /* do not allow top copying this class */
2697  MavlinkStreamHILActuatorControls(MavlinkStreamHILActuatorControls &) = delete;
2698  MavlinkStreamHILActuatorControls &operator = (const MavlinkStreamHILActuatorControls &) = delete;
2699 
2700 protected:
2701  explicit MavlinkStreamHILActuatorControls(Mavlink *mavlink) : MavlinkStream(mavlink),
2702  _status_sub(_mavlink->add_orb_subscription(ORB_ID(vehicle_status))),
2703  _act_sub(_mavlink->add_orb_subscription(ORB_ID(actuator_outputs))),
2704  _act_time(0)
2705  {}
2706 
2707  bool send(const hrt_abstime t)
2708  {
2709  actuator_outputs_s act;
2710 
2711  if (_act_sub->update(&_act_time, &act)) {
2712  vehicle_status_s status = {};
2713  _status_sub->update(&status);
2714 
2715  if ((status.timestamp > 0) && (status.arming_state == vehicle_status_s::ARMING_STATE_ARMED)) {
2716  /* translate the current system state to mavlink state and mode */
2717  uint8_t mavlink_state;
2718  uint8_t mavlink_base_mode;
2719  uint32_t mavlink_custom_mode;
2720  mavlink_hil_actuator_controls_t msg = {};
2721 
2722  get_mavlink_mode_state(&status, &mavlink_state, &mavlink_base_mode, &mavlink_custom_mode);
2723 
2724  const float pwm_center = (PWM_DEFAULT_MAX + PWM_DEFAULT_MIN) / 2;
2725 
2726  unsigned system_type = _mavlink->get_system_type();
2727 
2728  /* scale outputs depending on system type */
2729  if (system_type == MAV_TYPE_QUADROTOR ||
2730  system_type == MAV_TYPE_HEXAROTOR ||
2731  system_type == MAV_TYPE_OCTOROTOR ||
2732  system_type == MAV_TYPE_VTOL_DUOROTOR ||
2733  system_type == MAV_TYPE_VTOL_QUADROTOR ||
2734  system_type == MAV_TYPE_VTOL_RESERVED2) {
2735 
2736  /* multirotors: set number of rotor outputs depending on type */
2737 
2738  unsigned n;
2739 
2740  switch (system_type) {
2741  case MAV_TYPE_QUADROTOR:
2742  n = 4;
2743  break;
2744 
2745  case MAV_TYPE_HEXAROTOR:
2746  n = 6;
2747  break;
2748 
2749  case MAV_TYPE_VTOL_DUOROTOR:
2750  n = 2;
2751  break;
2752 
2753  case MAV_TYPE_VTOL_QUADROTOR:
2754  n = 4;
2755  break;
2756 
2757  case MAV_TYPE_VTOL_RESERVED2:
2758  n = 8;
2759  break;
2760 
2761  default:
2762  n = 8;
2763  break;
2764  }
2765 
2766  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 16; i++) {
2767  if (act.output[i] > PWM_DEFAULT_MIN / 2) {
2768  if (i < n) {
2769  /* scale PWM out 900..2100 us to 0..1 for rotors */
2770  msg.controls[i] = (act.output[i] - PWM_DEFAULT_MIN) / (PWM_DEFAULT_MAX - PWM_DEFAULT_MIN);
2771 
2772  } else {
2773  /* scale PWM out 900..2100 us to -1..1 for other channels */
2774  msg.controls[i] = (act.output[i] - pwm_center) / ((PWM_DEFAULT_MAX - PWM_DEFAULT_MIN) / 2);
2775  }
2776 
2777  } else {
2778  /* send 0 when disarmed and for disabled channels */
2779  msg.controls[i] = 0.0f;
2780  }
2781  }
2782 
2783  } else {
2784  /* fixed wing: scale throttle to 0..1 and other channels to -1..1 */
2785 
2786  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 16; i++) {
2787  if (act.output[i] > PWM_DEFAULT_MIN / 2) {
2788  if (i != 3) {
2789  /* scale PWM out 900..2100 us to -1..1 for normal channels */
2790  msg.controls[i] = (act.output[i] - pwm_center) / ((PWM_DEFAULT_MAX - PWM_DEFAULT_MIN) / 2);
2791 
2792  } else {
2793  /* scale PWM out 900..2100 us to 0..1 for throttle */
2794  msg.controls[i] = (act.output[i] - PWM_DEFAULT_MIN) / (PWM_DEFAULT_MAX - PWM_DEFAULT_MIN);
2795  }
2796 
2797  } else {
2798  /* set 0 for disabled channels */
2799  msg.controls[i] = 0.0f;
2800  }
2801  }
2802  }
2803 
2804  msg.time_usec = hrt_absolute_time();
2805  msg.mode = mavlink_base_mode;
2806  msg.flags = 0;
2807 
2808  mavlink_msg_hil_actuator_controls_send_struct(_mavlink->get_channel(), &msg);
2809 
2810  return true;
2811  }
2812  }
2813 
2814  return false;
2815  }
2816 };
